title: Breathtakingly Beautiful Res Lease in Austin. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ["Joseph's Corner is perfectly located in West Campus!", 'It is a quick walk to campus, but also just 1 block off 29th & Rio Grande making it attractive for non students as well!', 'Walk to countless coffee shops, restaurants, bars, etc. and enjoy all that Austin has to offer!', 'Boutique 8 -unit complex that is well kept and updated.', 'Among the features are balconies off each of the 3 bedrooms as well as a large common balcony outside the entry door.', 'Residents responsible for $100 (per unit) monthly charge that goes towards water, wastewater, gas & trash.', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 5247226)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas, All Prices)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'PRICES ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE DAILY/PICS MAY NOT REFLECT EXACT UNIT']
